OL,5, A major UK investment fund has said it 
OL,6, will vote to try to get directors      
OL,7, kicked out of firms that fail to make  
OL,8, good on environmental pledges.         
OL,10,FAviva Investors also wants bosses' pay 
OL,11,Fto be linked to sustainability goals.  
OL,13,FIt is the latest big investment firm to
OL,14,Framp up the pressure on corporations in
OL,15,Fa bid to make them clean up their acts.
OL,17,FBlackRock, the world's largest fund,   
OL,18,Fhas told the firms it invests in to    
OL,19,Fstep up on sustainability or face the  
OL,20,Fconsequences.                          
